# Tabiori — local environment example
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is gitignored) and fill in your key.
# Without a key the app still runs: search is disabled, and you can add spots by
# clicking the map. Reverse geocoding (address auto-fill) also requires a key.
#
# Get a free key at https://www.geoapify.com/ (check the current free-tier
# limits and usage policy). For public builds, restrict the key by allowed
# origin in the Geoapify dashboard — a frontend key can never be fully hidden
# from the shipped bundle.

VITE_GEOAPIFY_API_KEY=your-geoapify-api-key
